# Responsive Login Form

This project is a responsive login form created using HTML and CSS. It has a modern, professional design and includes features like input validation, hover effects, and social media login buttons. The form is fully responsive and adjusts to different screen sizes to provide a seamless user experience on both desktop and mobile devices.

## Features

- Clean and modern design
- Fully responsive layout
- Hover effects for buttons and links
- Social media login options
- Easy-to-understand and customizable CSS

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3



